{"tid":1801884,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【RTHK 突發】陳茂波：義士只是虛張聲勢    以「逆我者亡」方式損害法治","createTime":"2019-12-29T04:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T04:33:27.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b476457796e2666d2cbe2aadf020f4991497a878","tid":1801884,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:15:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500006-20191229.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500006-20191229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNUuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=3740dc9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500006-20191229.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=edc6220c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500006-20191229.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1500006_1_L_20191229113757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1500006_1_L_20191229113757.jpg&h=d616a099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長陳茂波發表網誌，表示今年出現暴力破壞情況，令市民減少外出及消費意欲，10月份本港零售銷售貨量銳減兩成六，是歷來最大單月跌幅，至於境外商務或觀光旅客亦受到嚇怕，即使平安夜及聖誕節等傳統旺季，入境人次亦減少約一半。餐飲服務業失業率已升至超過6%，是超過8年來最高。本港第三季經濟按年負增長2.9%的其中兩個百分點，便是暴力衝擊與社會動盪因素造成，第四季經濟繼續呈現負增長已無可避免。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波說，政府帳目15年以來首次見紅，意味著在經濟衰退下政府調動財政資源的靈活度會下降。<br />\n<br />\n他批評，暴徒以「逆我者亡」的原始暴力方式，恐嚇小市民的人身安全及言論自由，透過踐踏別人的自由與權利<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">虛張聲勢</span></span></strong>，亦損害了法治，無論有何動機，都不應該訴諸暴力，如默許和放任暴徒的凶殘行為，這才是真正毁掉香港的元凶。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波認為，必須全力阻止暴力脅迫和破壞行為，透過對話處理爭議，共謀出路，至於因內外交困引致的經濟衰退，亦要合力應對。陳茂波預期，貿易保護主義、單邊主義等仍會主導明年外圍形勢，而本地消費及旅遊能否早日改善，要視乎內部社會局勢能否盡快恢復平穩。"},{"pid":"63b07c5594cbd36f34c56fe8974260e5110d0332","tid":1801884,"uid":284463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:15:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈的障礙<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1801188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1801188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a0d0676b4107e7b905028b742176ed3574d41a0","tid":1801884,"uid":271123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:16:05.000Z","msg":"呢個禮拜講左幾多次？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7c1f35999573de4786a3c31f4805dc8f784c2f","tid":1801884,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:19:54.000Z","msg":"一個消滅自由嘅政權話人踐踏自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f64407bd40a63a6de56ebf2b20a03ceaf4117a8","tid":1801884,"uid":103981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"一個咁文明既地方由呢D人管治，真係不幸，香港人無乜運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52edde2c400a5b979c5b5f4041ed31ad6d19fe85","tid":1801884,"uid":121197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:20:51.000Z","msg":"將義士改做政府就fit晒"},{"pid":"1dfc13c2089dd681f62668c446b8c293a95f3f79","tid":1801884,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:20:59.000Z","msg":"逆我者亡講緊中共？"},{"pid":"c56a9fe493f2332a6c771a50b09650479603968e","tid":1801884,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:21:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">乜佢咁講支那共產黨</span>"},{"pid":"cb25a814a3257d3b4a631f5378c768751a76cbf4","tid":1801884,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T04:21:49.000Z","msg":"政犬只係虛張聲勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" 